    "For example, defect density and defect burn rate [36] can be employed in the \"Development\" step to monitor the quality of code being produced and the efficiency of defect resolution over time.Recent studies have identified several challenges when implementing the DevSecOps paradigm [5,114].",
    "For instance, Akbar et al. [5] pointed out challenges such as the use of immature automated deployment tools and a lack of software security awareness.",
